 style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 169.5px;\">Ox</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 54px; text-align: right;\">300</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 169.5px;\">Pig</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 54px; text-align: right;\">30</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 169.5px;\">Sheep</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 54px; text-align: right;\">15</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 211px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n<table style=\"height: 110px; float: left;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 25px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 25px; width: 185px; text-align: left;\">\n<h4><strong>Lodging</strong></h4>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 25px; width: 38.5px; text-align: right;\">\n<h4><strong>Cost</strong></h4>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 185px; text-align: left;\">Bed, per night</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 38.5px; text-align: right;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 185px; text-align: left;\">Private room, per night</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 38.5px; text-align: right;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 185px; text-align: left;\">Meal</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 38.5px; text-align: right;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 185px; text-align: left;\">Hot Bath</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 38.5px; text-align: right;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 185px; text-align: left;\">Stabling and fodder</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 38.5px; text-align: right;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 212.5px; vertical-align: top;\">\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<h4><strong>Ships</st